text: The Odenwaldkreis is a Kreis (district) in the south of Hesse, Germany. The district is in the Odenwald mountains. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Bad König #Breuberg #Erbach #Michelstadt #Oberzent #Brensbach #Brombachtal #Fränkisch-Crumbach #Höchst im Odenwald #Lützelbach #Mossautal #Reichelsheim ==References== Category:Districts of Hesse
